text: Vilém Goppold Jr. (15 August 1893 - 7 July 1945) was a Bohemian fencer. He competed in three events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1893 births Category:1945 deaths Category:Czech male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Bohemia Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics
